title: Winter World
description:
The survivors on a future planet Earth frozen over from pole to pole by an environmental disaster desperately struggle for survival. Scully, an amoral adventurer and a young orphan girl named Wynn strive to escape the roaming bands of raiders fighting over the items necessary for existence.

Published by Eclipse in 1987, written by Chuck Dixon and illustrated by Jorge Zaffino.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
